installationInstructions.author: Milton from Camp Hill, PA
installationInstructions.title: Broke a blade off of the fan
installationInstructions.content: When cleaning the coils on your refrigerator always remember rule number 1, unplug it first. I was cleaning the coils and hit the fan blade while it was moving with a brush, thus breaking off one of the fan blades. I ordered a new fan and installed it in about 15 minutes. Very easy repair.
